#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn17.34:0.2"
msgid "4. Catutthavagga"
msgstr "4. The Fourth Chapter"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 34. Sukkadhammasutta → sukkadhammasamucchedasuttaṃ (bj) | sukko (pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn17.34:0.3"
msgid "34. Sukkadhammasutta"
msgstr "34. Bright Quality"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn17.34:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

#. </p><p class="added">
msgctxt "sn17.34:1.2"
msgid "“Dāruṇo, bhikkhave, lābhasakkārasiloko."
msgstr "“Possessions, honor, and popularity are brutal …"

msgctxt "sn17.34:1.3"
msgid "Lābhasakkārasilokena abhibhūtassa pariyādiṇṇacittassa, bhikkhave, devadattassa sukko dhammo samucchedamagamā."
msgstr "Devadatta cut off his bright quality because his mind was overcome and overwhelmed by possessions, honor, and popularity."

msgctxt "sn17.34:1.4"
msgid "Evaṃ dāruṇo kho, bhikkhave, lābhasakkārasiloko … pe …"
msgstr "So brutal are possessions, honor, and popularity. …”"

msgctxt "sn17.34:1.5"
msgid "sikkhitabban”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn17.34:1.6"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
